replies.author: DreamVoid
replies.txt_content: 尝试删掉Askyblock文件夹里的comfig.yml文件然后asadmin reload

replies.author: EmptyLava
replies.txt_content:
你的空岛插件配置文件有一些选项没有被设置

你可以删除config.yml 让它自己生成
